title: Rob Bonta
added: On March 24, 2020, California Governor, Gavin Newsom, nominated Bonta as the state's Attorney General, replacing former Attorney General, Alex Padilla, who became Senator of California.  Padilla, replaced Kamala Harris, who became Vice President of the United States.
